      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. these are good. though i'm a bit worried about some people in my local community being weird about it or saying it's just \"political\" stuff. can u make the captions sound a bit more professional and less like they're taking a huge social stance? just want it to feel natural for a luxury brand without sounding like an activist.",
