      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, thanks. but i'm curious about what u said about \"alienating conservative customers.\" do u think it's actually possible to be truly inclusive and still appeal to everyone? or is the \"DEI\" thing inherently political and bound to divide people? i just want to make sure i'm not accidentally picking a side if i go through with this.",
